column1: ## This list is not for pedagogical purposes. This list is for research purposes to
## account for the coverage of a word and all its possible word forms. It is an
## attempt to account for all possible inflections of a word based on its part of speech.
## For example	the gerund form of verbs are occasionly found in the plural	such as
## buildings and paintings. Therefore all possible gerunds are also pluralized even
